                "answer": "<p>Yes. Game days are our busiest, so we recommend booking a table ahead of time. Reserve your spot through our Toast booking page and you're locked in before kickoff.</p>",
                "open_by_default": false
              },
              "blocks": {}
            },
            "ls_faq_item_GbFr4f": {
              "type": "ls-faq-item",
              "settings": {
                "question": "How do I reserve a table for a group?",
                "answer": "<p>Easy — book directly through our reservation page (powered by Toast). Pick your party size, date, and time, and you're set. For bigger groups or private setups, the Private Events form is the better route.</p>",
                "open_by_default": false
              },
              "blocks": {}
            },
            "ls_faq_item_fEnnFi": {
              "type": "ls-faq-item",
              "settings": {
                "question": "Is there a minimum party size to reserve?",
                "answer": "<p>Reservations work for groups of all sizes, especially on busy nights and game days. (Confirm any minimum party size or table-hold policy.)</p>",
                "open_by_default": false
              },
              "blocks": {}
            },
            "ls_faq_item_C3DLHR": {
              "type": "ls-faq-item",
              "settings": {
                "question": "Can I reserve rooftop seating?",
                "answer": "<p>Rooftop's first-come on most nights, but for groups and events we can often set it aside.</p>",
                "open_by_default": false
              },
              "blocks": {}
            }
